name: your future is an algorithm
description: additionally prcessed image still taken from a multiprocessed video file - originally created as reference for a 200 x 150 cm canvas commission (2016) [side note: the canvas was eventually destroyed] - this is a work that continues to pose not only the familiar question of 'what is art?' but additionally, 'who is the artist?' - technology is changing our conceptual understanding of reality |               Brendan Conrad Forde | @acid_very
